Package com.pandora.general.objects.services.implementations

package com.pandora.general.objects.services.implementations
This package contains service implementations for managing various aspects related to freshwater biogeochemistry within the Pandora model. These services are responsible for CRUD operations, data storage, and manipulation associated with different entities such as cells, rivers, timesteps, discharges, terrestrial sources, upstream sources, volumes, and state variables.

The package includes the following classes:

  • CellTimestepMapCrudService:

    Service for CRUD operations on a map of CellTimestep objects.

  • DischargesMapServiceImpl:

    Service for managing discharge data associated with a Cell and a LocalDateTime.

  • RiverMapCrudService:

    Service for CRUD operations on a map of River objects.

  • RiverTimestepMapCrudService:

    Service for CRUD operations on a map of RiverTimestep objects.

  • TerrestrialSourcesMapServiceImpl:

    Service for managing terrestrial sources data associated with a Cell and a LocalDateTime.

  • UpstreamSourcesMapServiceImpl:

    Service for managing upstream sources data associated with a Cell and a LocalDateTime, utilizing an injected TransportCalculationService.

  • VolumesMapServiceImpl:

    Service for managing volume data associated with a Cell and a LocalDateTime.

  • YMapServiceImpl:

    Service for managing state variable data associated with a Cell and a LocalDateTime.

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    CellMapCrudService
    CellMapCrudService is an implementation of the AbstractBaseMapCrudService class, providing CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for managing Cell objects.
    CellTimestepMapCrudService
    CellTimestepMapCrudService is an implementation of the AbstractBaseMapCrudService class, providing CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for managing CellTimestep objects.
    DischargesMapServiceImpl
    DischargesMapServiceImpl is an implementation of the DischargesMapService interface, providing services related to managing discharge values associated with specific Cell locations and LocalDateTime timestamps.
    RiverMapCrudService
    RiverMapCrudService is an implementation of the AbstractBaseMapCrudService class, providing CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for managing River objects.
    RiverTimestepMapCrudService
    RiverTimestepMapCrudService is an implementation of the AbstractBaseMapCrudService class, providing CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for managing RiverTimestep objects.
    TerrestrialSourcesMapServiceImpl
    TerrestrialSourcesMapServiceImpl is an implementation of the TerrestrialSourcesMapService interface, providing services related to managing terrestrial sources data associated with specific Cell locations and LocalDateTime timestamps.
    UpstreamSourcesMapServiceImpl
    UpstreamSourcesMapServiceImpl is an implementation of the UpstreamSourcesMapService interface, providing services related to managing upstream sources data associated with specific Cell locations and LocalDateTime timestamps.
    VolumesMapServiceImpl
    VolumesMapServiceImpl is an implementation of the VolumesMapService interface, providing services related to managing volume data associated with specific Cell locations and LocalDateTime timestamps.
    YMapServiceImpl
    YMapServiceImpl is an implementation of the YMapService interface, providing services related to managing state variable data associated with specific Cell locations and LocalDateTime timestamps.
